(1, 1, 34, 'https://yamaha-ai-generations-2026.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/generations/gen_a66d118c557e4071bb58155d1b4bd89d.jpg', '{\"behavior\":2,\"destination_id\":702,\"destination\":\"Brazil\",\"destination_meta\":{\"country\":\"Brazil\",\"country_bn\":\"ব্রাজিল\",\"jersey_colors\":\"vibrant yellow and green\",\"theme_colors\":\"yellow and green\",\"stadium\":\"Maracanã Stadium\",\"personality\":\"Proud Brazil supporter, yellow and green football spirit.\",\"personality_bn\":\"গর্বিত ব্রাজিল সমর্থক, ফুটবল উদ্দীপনা।\",\"scene\":\"Outside Maracanã Stadium, damp pavement, soft stadium lighting. Brazil flag in the sky. blurred crowds in the distant background wearing vibrant yellow and green jerseys. yellow and green confetti. festive banners.\"},\"aspiration_id\":20,\"aspiration\":\"All-Round Rider\",\"aspiration_meta\":{\"color\":\"White\"}}', 'Embodying the vibrant spirit of the Seleção, you command the road with the same passion that fuels a nation\'s football pride. Your Yamaha Fazer stands as the perfect companion for a rider who carries the gold and green legacy with such effortless grace.', '2026-06-10 19:23:23', 'a66d118c557e4071bb58155d1b4bd89d', 'completed', 2, 702, 20, 'Black', '{\"strategy\":\"weighted_distribution_with_color_bonus\",\"aspiration_color\":\"White\",\"total_behavior_generations\":0,\"candidates\":[{\"bike_id\":34,\"model_name\":\"Yamaha Fazer\",\"weight_percent\":50,\"priority_order\":3,\"assigned_count\":0,\"matched_color\":\"Black\",\"color_match\":false,\"deficit\":0.5,\"final_score\":0.505},{\"bike_id\":36,\"model_name\":\"Yamaha FZS V2\",\"weight_percent\":50,\"priority_order\":5,\"assigned_count\":0,\"matched_color\":\"Blue\",\"color_match\":false,\"deficit\":0.5,\"final_score\":0.505}]}', 'Create a cinematic lifestyle portrait of the exact person from the reference image. Preserve exact facial identity, hairstyle, facial hair, age, and natural likeness. Vertical 3:4 composition. Full body visible. Full motorcycle visible. Face unobstructed. Helmet not worn. Gender guidance: Use realistic male body structure, natural masculine posture, accurate body proportions, and clean rider styling while preserving the exact person from the reference image. Pose: Sitting sideways on the motorcycle seat, one foot on the ground, upper body turned slightly toward camera, one hand resting on or holding the helmet. Vehicle: realistic Yamaha Fazer in Black, with authentic model presence, accurate proportions, clean frame geometry, realistic materials, proper reflections, detailed mechanical parts, and high-quality motorcycle styling. Environment: Outside Maracanã Stadium, damp pavement, soft stadium lighting. Brazil flag in the sky. blurred crowds in the distant background wearing vibrant yellow and green jerseys. yellow and green confetti. festive banners. Mood: Proud Brazil supporter, yellow and green football spirit. All-Round Rider Wardrobe: vibrant yellow and green jersey of Brazil, optional fan scarf, dark denim jeans, premium sneakers. Clean and camera-ready. Style: commercial motorcycle photography, cinematic depth of field, natural lighting, realistic shadows, high-detail textures, realistic skin tones, and seamless face integration. Negative prompt: torn clothing, damaged trousers, worn-out shoes, dirty outfit, messy wardrobe, broken accessories, deformed motorcycle, warped motorcycle frame, rusty motorcycle parts, low-quality motorcycle detailing, blurry details, distorted anatomy, extra limbs, awkward hands, unnatural posture, multiple people around the bike, duplicated body parts, oversaturated colors, poorly rendered helmet, floating objects, cluttered background, cartoon appearance, illustration look, CGI-looking skin, bike number plate, rusted pipe.', '{\"textModel\":\"gemini-3.1-flash-lite\",\"textTokens\":{\"prompt\":717,\"candidates\":252},\"textCost\":0.0011145,\"textApiKeyIndex\":0,\"imageModel\":\"gemini-3.1-flash-image\",\"imageTokens\":{\"prompt\":1277,\"candidates\":1385},\"imageCost\":0.0047935,\"imageApiKeyIndex\":1,\"totalCost\":0.005908,\"totalDurationMs\":29728,\"checkpoints\":{\"form-data-parsed\":5,\"auth-verified\":8,\"rate-limit-checked\":20,\"photo-encoded\":21,\"persona-parsed\":21,\"bike-selected\":31,\"user-profile-loaded\":32,\"generation-reserved\":37,\"s3-uploaded\":29727},\"error\":null,\"optimizedPromptText\":\"A cinematic, full-body commercial lifestyle portrait of the man from the reference image, maintaining his exact facial identity, hairstyle, and masculine physique. He is seated sideways on a sleek black Yamaha Fazer, one foot planted firmly on the ground with a relaxed, confident posture, holding his helmet in one hand. He is dressed in a vibrant yellow and green Brazil football jersey, dark denim jeans, and premium sneakers. The scene is set outside the iconic Maracanã Stadium at night, with damp pavement reflecting soft stadium lights, festive banners, and subtle yellow and green confetti in the air. The background features a softly blurred crowd in team colors under a sky subtly accented with the Brazil flag. The shot is captured with a high-end photography aesthetic, focusing on sharp mechanical details of the motorcycle, rich skin textures, and a cinematic depth of field, exuding a proud, festive, and professional atmosphere.\"}'),
