(414, 381, 35, 'https://yamaha-ai-generations-2026.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/generations/gen_85e3aa1487413b962d752aaabedfb7c1.jpg', '{\"behavior\":13,\"destination_id\":709,\"destination\":\"Senegal\",\"destination_meta\":{\"country\":\"Senegal\",\"country_bn\":\"সেনেগাল\",\"jersey_colors\":\"white and green\",\"theme_colors\":\"green and yellow\",\"stadium\":\"Stade Abdoulaye Wade\",\"personality\":\"Proud Senegal supporter, green and yellow football spirit.\",\"personality_bn\":\"গর্বিত সেনেগাল সমর্থক, ফুটবল উদ্দীপনা।\",\"scene\":\"Outside Stade Abdoulaye Wade, damp pavement, soft stadium lighting. Senegal flag in the sky. blurred crowds in the distant background wearing white and green jerseys. green and yellow confetti. festive banners.\"},\"aspiration_id\":8,\"aspiration\":\"Energy Rider\",\"aspiration_meta\":{\"color\":\"Red\"}}', 'The spirited convergence of Senegalese pride and mechanical precision finds its ultimate expression in this striking portrait. Captured with the poise of an energy rider, the synergy between the vibrant heritage of the nation and the sleek architecture of the Yamaha FZ-25 creates a narrative of unstoppable momentum.', '2026-06-12 15:47:11', '85e3aa1487413b962d752aaabedfb7c1', 'completed', 13, 709, 8, 'Black', '{\"strategy\":\"weighted_distribution_with_color_bonus\",\"aspiration_color\":\"Red\",\"total_behavior_generations\":55,\"candidates\":[{\"bike_id\":35,\"model_name\":\"Yamaha FZ-25\",\"weight_percent\":25,\"priority_order\":3,\"assigned_count\":13,\"matched_color\":\"Black\",\"color_match\":false,\"deficit\":1,\"final_score\":1.0025},{\"bike_id\":39,\"model_name\":\"Yamaha FZX\",\"weight_percent\":30,\"priority_order\":1,\"assigned_count\":16,\"matched_color\":\"Matt Copper\",\"color_match\":false,\"deficit\":0.8,\"final_score\":0.803},{\"bike_id\":34,\"model_name\":\"Yamaha Fazer\",\"weight_percent\":25,\"priority_order\":4,\"assigned_count\":14,\"matched_color\":\"Red\",\"color_match\":true,\"deficit\":0,\"final_score\":0