(742, 5, 'Curaçao', 'Support Curaçao in World Cup 2026.', '', '{\"country\":\"Curaçao\",\"country_bn\":\"কুরাসাও\",\"jersey_colors\":\"blue and yellow\",\"theme_colors\":\"blue and yellow\",\"stadium\":\"Ergilio Hato Stadium\",\"personality\":\"Proud Curaçao supporter, blue and yellow football spirit.\",\"personality_bn\":\"গর্বিত কুরাসাও সমর্থক, ফুটবল উদ্দীপনা।\",\"scene\":\"Outside Ergilio Hato Stadium, damp pavement, soft stadium lighting. Curaçao flag in the sky. blurred crowds in the distant background wearing blue and yellow jerseys. blue and yellow confetti. festive banners.\"}', '2026-06-09 22:30:54', 'কুরাসাও', '২০২৬ বিশ্বকাপে কুরাসাও দলকে সমর্থন করুন।', 1),
(743, 5, 'Haiti', 'Support Haiti in World Cup 2026.', '', '{\"country\":\"Haiti\",\"country_bn\":\"হাইতি\",\"jersey_colors\":\"blue and red\",\"theme_colors\":\"blue and red\",\"stadium\":\"Stade Sylvio Cator\",\"personality\":\"Proud Haiti supporter, blue and red football spirit.\",\"personality_bn\":\"গর্বিত হাইতি সমর্থক, ফুটবল উদ্দীপনা।\",\"scene\":\"Outside Stade Sylvio Cator, damp pavement, soft stadium lighting. Haiti flag in the sky. blurred crowds in the distant background wearing blue and red jerseys. blue and red confetti. festive banners.\"}', '2026-06-09 22:30:54', 'হাইতি', '২০২৬ বিশ্বকাপে হাইতি দলকে সমর্থন করুন।', 1),
(744, 5, 'New Zealand', 'Support New Zealand in World Cup 2026.', '', '{\"country\":\"New Zealand\",\"country_bn\":\"নিউজিল্যান্ড\",\"jersey_colors\":\"all-black or white with black trim\",\"theme_colors\":\"black and white\",\"stadium\":\"Eden Park\",\"personality\":\"Proud New Zealand supporter, black and white football spirit.\",\"personality_bn\":\"গর্বিত নিউজিল্যান্ড সমর্থক, ফুটবল উদ্দীপনা।\",\"scene\":\"Outside Eden Park, damp pavement, soft stadium lighting. New Zealand flag in the sky. blurred crowds in the distant background wearing all-black or white with black trim jerseys. black and white confetti. festive banners.\"}', '2026-06-09 22:30:54', 'নিউজিল্যান্ড', '২০২৬ বিশ্বকাপে নিউজিল্যান্ড দলকে সমর্থন করুন।', 1);
